<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <title>Course Review Result - Rejected</title>
    <style>
      body {
        font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
        line-height: 1.6;
        color: #333;
      }
      .container {
        max-width: 600px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        padding: 20px;
      }
      .header {
        text-align: center;
        margin-bottom: 30px;
      }
      .content {
        margin-bottom: 30px;
      }
      .footer {
        text-align: center;
        font-size: 14px;
        color: #666;
      }
      .reason {
        background-color: #f8f8f8;
        padding: 15px;
        border-left: 4px solid #dc3545;
        margin: 20px 0;
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="container">
      <div class="header">
        <h2>Course Review Result</h2>
      </div>
      <div class="content">
        <p>Dear <%= userName %>,</p>

        <p>
          We regret to inform you that your course "<strong
            ><%= courseName %></strong
          >" has been reviewed and could not be approved at this time.
        </p>

        <div class="reason">
          <p><strong>Reason for Rejection:</strong></p>
          <p><%= comment %></p>
        </div>

        <p>
          You are welcome to make the necessary adjustments and submit the
          course again for review. If you need any clarification about the
          rejection reason, please don't hesitate to contact our support team.
        </p>

        <p>Thank you for your understanding.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="footer">
        <p>Need help? Contact us at <%= supportEmail %></p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
